&lt;p&gt;The concept is rather simple, you book a pay what you want shoot packet, I deliver the results and you choose how much you want to pay for the package.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This option is only possible on a fixed package.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The “Pay what you want” package contains:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A portrait shoot of 1 hour (business, casual, family, couple,…)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;on location (at home, work, in the park, …)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All selected photos delivered digitally through dropbox&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If you have questions about how this all works, you can check out the following blogposts &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.pitslamp.com/blog/20121128_faq-i-shoot-you-decide&#34;&gt;FAQ: I shoot, you decide&lt;/a&gt; But if you have any other questions, contact me.&lt;/p&gt;

